high_descs: Turn to the left, walk past the fridge, turn to the right and face the table.
Grab the black, dirty dish from the table.
Turn to the right, walk past the fridge, turn to the right again and approach the sink.
Wash the dirty dish in the sink with clean water.
Turn left twice, walk to the fridge, turn right again and walk to the shelf.
Put the clean dish on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Wash the dirty dish on the table with clean water and put it on the shelf.

high_descs: Go towards the fridge then turn left then right and go past the fridge then turn right and to to the round table
Pick up the dirty plate from the table
Turn right, then turn right again, then go to the left past the fridge then turn right and go to the sink
Put the plate in the sink and turn on the water, then turn off the water and take the plate out of the sink
Turn around and go to the fridge, then turn right and go to the shelving unit
Put the plate on the second shelf from the bottom
anns.task_desc: Put a washed plate onto a shelving unit

high_descs: Walk forward two wall, turn right, walk forward to table
Pick up dirty plate from table
Turn around, walk forward to counter, turn left, walk forward to refrigerator, turn right, walk forward to sink
Put dirty plate in sink, turn on water, turn off water, remove plate from sink
Turn around, walk to refrigerator, turn right, walk forward to wall
Place plate on second shelf against wall
anns.task_desc: Pick up dirty plate, clean it and finally put it away
